    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-Prepare-environment"><a href="#1-Prepare-environment" class="headerlink" title="1. Prepare environment"></a>1. Prepare environment</h1><h2 id="1-1-hexo"><a href="#1-1-hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.1 hexo"></a>1.1 hexo</h2><p>hexo download</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">$ npm install hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span> -g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-2-blog-floder"><a href="#1-2-blog-floder" class="headerlink" title="1.2 blog floder"></a>1.2 blog floder</h2><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-variable">$</span> hexo init username.github.io<br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> username.github.io<br><span class="hljs-variable">$</span> npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-3-static-pages"><a href="#1-3-static-pages" class="headerlink" title="1.3 static pages"></a>1.3 static pages</h2><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crystal"><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo clean<br><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>g means generate</p><h2 id="1-4-hexo-run-locally"><a href="#1-4-hexo-run-locally" class="headerlink" title="1.4 hexo run locally"></a>1.4 hexo run locally</h2><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crystal"><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>s means server, open local <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> will see the pages</p><h1 id="2-New-post"><a href="#2-New-post" class="headerlink" title="2. New post"></a>2. New post</h1><h2 id="2-1-command-way"><a href="#2-1-command-way" class="headerlink" title="2.1 command way"></a>2.1 command way</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">hexo new  <span class="hljs-built_in">test</span></span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>there will be <code>test.md</code> under <code>source/_posts</code>, see pages by following commands</p><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crystal"><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo clean<br><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo g<br><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-2-direct-way"><a href="#2-2-direct-way" class="headerlink" title="2.2 direct way"></a>2.2 direct way</h2><p>new markfile justr under folder <code>source/_posts</code></p><h1 id="3-Theme"><a href="#3-Theme" class="headerlink" title="3 Theme"></a>3 Theme</h1><h1 id="4-Deploy-to-github"><a href="#4-Deploy-to-github" class="headerlink" title="4 Deploy to github"></a>4 Deploy to github</h1><h2 id="4-1-download-hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#4-1-download-hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="4.1 download hexo-deployer-git"></a>4.1 download hexo-deployer-git</h2><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git <span class="hljs-comment">--save</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-2-config"><a href="#4-2-config" class="headerlink" title="4.2 config"></a>4.2 config</h2><p>change file in <code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repo:</span> <span class="hljs-params">&lt;repository url&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> [branch]<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>repo is the username.github.io repository url, usually like this <code>https://github.com/username/username.github.io.git</code></p><p>branch usually is the <code>master</code> branch</p><h2 id="4-3-deploy"><a href="#4-3-deploy" class="headerlink" title="4.3 deploy"></a>4.3 deploy</h2><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crystal"><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>d refres to <code>deploy</code></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
